
Purpose: Improved display over top due to 
Usage
$ htop
NOTE: auto sorted by CPU usage, 

Kill a Process
$ htop
select process with arrow keys
kill with F9

Change Proces Priority
$ htop
select process with arrow keys
lower priority with F7, raise with F8

Change Process Display Order
$ htop
press F6
select column order

Installation
$ sudo yum install -y epel-release
$ sudo yum install -y update
$ sudo yum install -y htop
